title: Seshadripuram Degree and Post Graduation College | Faculty
content: Seshadripuram First Grade College Yelahanka, Bengaluru Permanently affiliated to Dr. Manmohan Singh Bengaluru City Universityand recognized by UGC under 2(f) & 12(B) NAAC accredited A+Grade ISO 9001:2015 Certified The college has quality human resources in its teaching and administrative staff. The teaching staff is a good mixture of experience and energy. Of course, there is a plenty of talent in both categories. More than one third of teachers have taught for two decades and another one third have completed a decade of teaching. For last several years, the department has been soliciting the services of the Principal, the faculty and the college for successfully conducting seminars, academic workshops, preparation of question papers, preparation of curriculum, syllabus and text books and conduct of District level examination, practical level of examination, District and State level sports and cultural activities etc. This speaks of the niche the college has covered for itself in the world of MBA Education in the State. Apart from huge experience and academic competence, the staff is endowed with empathy, love, and concern for the student community. Often, the former students bondly remember the humane bond that exists between the students and a large number of teachers. The resources at the disposal of the MBA programme are comparable with the best in the country: Digital Library, Seminar Hall, Audio - Visual Rooms, Conference Rooms, Computer Labs, Sports Club, Canteen and Banking facilities. Picturesque, conveniently located and spacious campus; large, well ventilated class rooms with fiber glass boards, LCD and OHP; well- equipped science laboratories; a state of the art business lab; extensive play grounds; lift and ramps, conference halls, infra structurally there is everything here to facilitate learning. This speaks of the niche the college has covered for itself in the world of MBA Education in the State.

Apart from huge experience and academic competence, the staff is endowed with empathy, love, and concern for the student community. Often, the former students bondly remember the humane bond that exists between the students and a large number of teachers.

The resources at the disposal of the MBA programme are comparable with the best in the country: Digital Library, Seminar Hall, Audio - Visual Rooms, Conference Rooms, Computer Labs, Sports Club, Canteen and Banking facilities.

Picturesque, conveniently located and spacious campus; large, well ventilated class rooms with fiber glass boards, LCD and OHP; well- equipped science laboratories; a state of the art business lab; extensive play grounds; lift and ramps, conference halls, infra structurally there is everything here to facilitate learning.
